Package: mclustCompositional
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-07
Title: Model-Based Clustering and Density Estimation for Compositional Data
Description: Model-based clustering and density estimation for compositional
    data using transformation-based Gaussian mixtures. The package applies an
    isometric log-ratio transformation to positive compositional observations,
    fits Gaussian mixture models with mclust, and evaluates densities on the
    original compositional scale.
